////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////
                   SNES Tips, Tricks and Cheats compilation
 ///////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////
     /\/POWER HOUSE/\/            -MAY '92-            /\/POWER HOUSE/\/  
 ///////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////
                            compiled by  BLOWTORCH>>
////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////////

ACTRAISER> Special Mode - To play only the action scenes all you have to do is
           finish the game once and then if you move the cursor down at the
           title screen the words SPECIAL MODE will appear.  Hit START and you
           will be able to play thru only the action scenes.
 
BIG RUN>   Option Mode  - There is a way to adjust the game play in this
           intense driver.  To set the controller how you want it just press
           SELECT at the title screen.

CASTLEBVANIA IV> Secret Passwords - These passcodes will let you reach all of
                 the levels and for the final boss, Dracula.  Do NOT enter
                 any name on the password screen.  H is heart.  A is axe.  P
                 is potion.  A "-" is a space.  
 
 2nd Quest    
  Level 1    Level 2    Level 3    Level 4    Level 5    Level 6
   HA-P       ----       ---A       ---P       ----       ----
   A--H       P---       P---       PP--       P---       PP--
   -A--       ----       ----       -P-A       ---A       -P-A
   -H--       P---       H---       ----       PA--       PA-- 
    
  Level 7    Level 8    Level 9    Level A    Level B    Last Level
   ---P       ----       ---A       ---H       ---A       ---P
   PH--       PP--       PP--       PH--       P---       PP--
   -H-P       -P-P       -P-P       -H-H       ---H       -P--
   -A--       PP--       HP--       AP--       HH--       -HA-
 
Bonus Rooms - There are Bonus Rooms in levels 3-1, 6-2 and 9-2.  Many power
              ups are in these rooms.

Invisible Staircase - On the level right before Dracuala there is a stair
              case leading into his domain.  There is also a massive drop
              from the platform into the depths of the uknown.  Luckily
              things are not what they seem.  If you take a large jump off
              the edge of the platform you will find yourself on an invisible
              ledge that will lead down some stairs going to the left.  Go
              as far as you can to the left and power-ups will fall in large
              quantities.  Collect 99 hearts, a triple boomerang and the best
              whip.  Be careful of falling off the edge when going back.

DARIUS TWIN>  49 Extra Ships - First make sure controller 2 is plugged in.  In
              the screen where you select one, two players or option, just 
              hold the L and R buttons on the second controller, press select
              and start on the first controller.  Before you do this, you may
              choose to grant one or two players with 49 lives each.

FINAL FIGHT>  Option Mode - At the title screen hold the L and R buttons at the
              top of the pad and press START.

F-ZERO>  Gain Lap Time - In Port Town II, there is a way to get ahead of the
         competition!  Get a Super Jet, then head to the left after passing
         the finish line.  Activate the Super Jet just before you get to the
         jump ramp and quickly angle to the right to fly to the opposite side
         of the track!

         Get a head start - To get a quick headstart hold down you accelerator
         button to take the lead.  Get right in front.  Once you take the lead
         one of the cars will ram you from behind thus giving you a super
         boost of speed.

GRADIUS III>  Extra Credits - At the title screen, press the X button about 16
              times per second and the credits will increase.  If you're fast
              enough you'll get 9 credits.
  
              Arcade Mode - For an additional challenge, go to the option mode
              and when in Game Level press the A button as fast as you can 
              until Arcade Mode appears.

              30 Extra Ships - At the title screen just hold LEFT and hit the
              A button 3 times.  When you start the game you will have 30
              ships.

              Trick Full Power UP - Pause the game and use the old familiar
              UP, UP, DOWN, DOWN, LEFT, RIGHT, LEFT, RIGHT, B, A, and unpause.
              You will explode as this is a boobytrap from the programmers for
              those trying to cheat...hehe.

              REAL Full Power UP - Pause the game and press UP, UP, DOWN, DOWN,
              (now here's the trick,use the L and R buttons at the top of the
              controller) L, R, L, R, B, A, and unpause for a full set of 
              weapons.
              
              Reset From Controller - Tired of getting up to reset your 
              machine?  Hold buttons L, R, and START at the same time and 
              then press SELECT to reset your game.     

HOLE IN ONE GOLF>  If you want to see a hole in one, just enter the following
                   codes in the "Memory Shot" option.
 
                   CQJB83CFDFJ#H?LBBT7BJCF  or  B!5B9GB5SFGB3J5BB?GBMYQ

                   Metal Woods - Start the game and go the screen where you
                   enter your name.  Put in METAL PLAY as your name(leave a
                   space in betweent the words) and exit the screen by going
                   to "OK".  Confirm your choice be clicking "OK" again.  
                   You should see metal clubs in the lower left hand corner
                   of your screen and you can now use these to hit the ball
                   a greater distance.
    
                   Sound Test - Enter 'Bgm' at the memory shot password screen
                   to enter a sound test mode.     

HYPER ZONE>  Sound Test - At the title screen, just hold the top L and R
             buttons and press START. A sound test will appear on the screen.
             Pick any one of the sound effects or music tracks from the game
             and press A to hear them.

JOE AND MAC> Hidden Levels - In Level 8 there is a red egg in the middle of
             the level.  Kill all of the small dinosaurs before you crack
             the egg and you will be flown to a hidden bonus level in which
             you can power-up your weapon and collect a key to get you in
             blue dots on the map.  Also, in level 9, there will be a red
             egg in the beginning of the level.  Crack it and you will be
             taken to another hidden level.

             Get Back in Dinosaur - When you are inside the dinosaur in the
             last stage, there is a way you can continue right back inside him
             if you die.  When you are asked to continue, select "YES" and you
             will be shown on the map in the last white "continue" spot.  Go to
             the last stage and when you are in it, press START to pause the
             game, and then SELECT.  You will automatically be transported 
             inside the dinosaur without having to go through the stage and
             fight him all over again.

JOHN MADDEN FOOTBALL>  Close up Trick - When the title screen shows, hold down
                       and any button and then press START several times to get
                       past the screens.  Once you do this, the screen will go
                       blank for a couple of seconds and then you will get a 
                       closeup of the fans.  Just let go of the button to start
                       the game.

THE LEGEND OF MYSTICAL NINJA> Continue Codes - Here are all of the codes to 
                              continue.  These will get you to the beginning
