PAPERBOY 2>  Start on Higher Level - To start this game on the "HARD WAY"
             go to the route option on the player select screen and enter
             the code: 6479 by pressing right on the control pad.  

PILOT WINGS>  Level Codes -  Level 1 - 000000
                             Level 2 - 985206
                             Level 3 - 394391
                             Level 4 - 520771
                             Heli    - 108048
         
              Expert level - Level 6 - 400718
                             Level 7 - 773224
                             Level 8 - 165411
                             Level 9 - 760357
                             Heli    - 882943

              Bonus Stages - Get to the bonus stages by accomplishing special
              maneuvers on the Rocketbelt and Parachute rounds.  Ignore the
              rings and other objectives in these rounds and maneuver your
              character over the moving platform in each level.  If you can
              land on this portion of the target area, you will be taken to
              the bonus stage with a perfect rating of 100 points!
                   When you are using the Rocketbelt and get this bonus, you
              will be transformed into a winged man!  While in this special
              mode, try to jump onto the trampolines and hit the power P's
              before landing in the middle of the target.
                   When you enter the bonus stage in the parachute rounds,
              you transform into a penguin who must high dive into a multi-
              point pool!  The waters are separated by ropes which each
              designate different extra point values.

POPULOUS>  Full Power - At any time Press A then B.  Now hold Left and Press
           Right and Press A, B, X in that order and then hit SELECT. Go to
           the swamp icon. If it hasn't turned red then you have FULL POWER!

RANMA 1/2>  To play against the computer using ANY of the characters just 
            press BOTH the R and L buttons while pressing START.  

SIMCITY>  Bonus Gift Trick - Pick a land with plenty of water in it,but 
          do not pick an island.  Make sure you pick a land with water
          near the middle.  Now, create roads, find the middle of the 
          land and make a cross with these roads all the way to the edge
          of the map of you land.  Do not connect the cross in the middle
          of the water, or the trick will not work.  Once you make a 
          cross with these roads near a body of water, you will be able
          to build anywhere from two to five casinos or amusement parks!

          More Maps - Select "Start New City" on the menu screen, then choose
          any map number between 1 and 999.  "Ok" the map you want. Go into
          the map and choose the "Go to Menu" icon at the top of the screen.
          Do NOT save this.  Choose "Start New City" again on the menu screen.
          Wait, and the same map that you chose earlier will turn out to be
          a different map with the same number!  This works all the way from 
          map 1 to 999, giving you a total for 1998 instead of the regular 
          999.
                 
SMASH TV> Life and Continue Increase - Go to the player/skill selection
          screen and push the control pad down to the level of skill.  Now,
          press and hold the L button.  While holding the L button, press
          and hold the R button. With these held down, press UP on the
          control pad.  You will hear "BINGO" and a screen should appear
          that will let you increase your lives and credits to continue.
 
          Super Sound Test - First go the the player/skill select screen and
          then press the two top buttons on the controller in this order: L,
          R, L, L, R.  You will hear the voice say, "BINGO" and then you will
          be brought to the theme music section and sound select screen!

SUPER EARTH DEFENSE FORCE>  Invincibility Code - During play press START to
                            pause the game and then press A, B, X, Y, L and
                            R, then Up, Dn, Left, Right on the directional
                            pad.  This has to be done at the beginning of
                            each stage.
   
                            Weird Scrolling Title - Plug the 2nd controller.
                            Before you turn on the SNES, hold the 2nd control
                            pad in the UP position and hold START at the same
                            time. You will see the title scroll in a different
                            manner than normal.

SUPER OFF ROAD>  Unlimited Continues - First plug in both controllers. Next,
                 select a 2 player game and play as the red truck, but let
                 the blue truck stand still.  When the race ends, you will be
                 in third place, which will automatically put you in the next
                 race.  The unused blue truck will always be able to continue.

SUPER GHOULS AND GHOSTS>  Stage Select and Sound Test - Make sure both 
                          controllers are plugged in.  Go to the option screen
                          and move the cursor to the exit. Now instead of
                          exiting, hold button L and START simulataneously on
                          the 2nd controller and press START on the 1st.  You
                          will find yourself on a special screen which you can
                          select stages, area, sound effects and music.

SUPER R-TYPE>  Weapon Select and Full Power Up - Begin this trick at the title
               screen by pressing DOWN, R, RIGHT, DOWN, RIGHT, RIGHT, DOWN,
               RIGHT, DOWN, DOWN.  You will hear a noise like the start chime
               then press START to begin the game.  After the game has started
               pause it, and hit R, RIGHT, DOWN, Y, DOWN, RIGHT, DOWN, LEFT,
               RIGHT, DOWN, RIGHT, RIGHT, and then press the buttons for the
               laser FIRST, AND THEN a missile.  After you have done this un-
               pause and take out the enemy!
 
               Level Select - Hold down the 'R' button on the top of the 
               control and press UP on the pad nine times.  You will hear a
               tone that indicates that the level select has been activated.
               Now press START and the pause the game.  Hold the 'R' button
               down while at the same time depressing the 'A' button.  While
               holding both buttons down, press SELECT.  In the lower left
               hand corner of the screen you will see a set of numbers
               indicating on what level play will begin.  Simply press UP or
               DOWN on the control pad to select from any game level!

SUPER TENNIS>  Start in Final Game - To see the ending screen and be a winner
               in every tournament as 'AMY', enter the following code.  You
               will have to win the New York Open, which is the final game.
 
                             08QCMVF RHRMSYY
                             RHYH9QX J0VYQYH
                             4HR0CQ1 4065C6P
                             DJSSSRL MM8

               Advanced Player - Start the game like normal, but when you
               begin, press SELECT on controller 1 before you serve.  Now on
               controller 2, press these buttons in this order:  R, R, LEFT,
               DOWN, B, A, L and L.  You should then hear the crowd cheer.
               Back on controller 1, press A or B and you should see some
               numbers and letters on the screen.  Change all of these numbers
               and letters to the letter F using the X and B buttons on
               controller 1, and you will have a pro who is fast and very
               accurate.

SUPER MARIO WORLD>  too many tips for this game!!!  If you don't know them
                    get yourself some help!!!

THUNDER SPIRITS>  Option Screen - This is an option mode trick.  Hold the L
                  button on the top of the controller and the SELECT button
                  at the same time.  While holding these, press START and
                  you will be brought to an option screen which will give
                  you many features to improve your game.

TOP RACER>  Some passwords for Top Gear in Professional Mode.
 
            USA - FOUR MEG          SCANDINAVIA - ALCHEMY
            S. AMERICA- LEGEND      FRANCE - LOOPER
            JAPAN - THE WORLD       ITALY - SEASONAL
            GERMANY - LETS RACE
           

UN SQUADRON>  Extra Difficulty Setting - If you think that you are good at
              the game UN SQUADRON try it at this new difficulty setting.
              Plug in the 2nd controller.  Go to the option screen with the
              1st controller and highlight the difficulty setting.  Now
              with the 2nd controller, hold down the A and X buttons and
              while these are held down, change the difficulty with the 1st
              controller.  You should see a new level called "GAMER".

ULTRAMAMN> Special Option Screen - Press SELECT and START together at the
           title screen.  The option mode will allow you to adjust the
           difficulty setting and enter a sound test.

Y's III>  Invisibility Code - Begin a game and press reset on your machine.
          When the American Sammy logo appears, use controller 2 and press
          UP, DOWN, UP, DOWN, SELECT and START before the logo fades out.
          When the continue screen comes up, select "continue" on controller 1
          and go into any previously saved area.  Press SELECT to display
          screen and then go to the status screen.  When the status screen
          shows up, press START on controller 2.  The word "debug" should
          appear next to the status.  When you continue your game, you will
          be invincible!

ZELDA III>  Once again, too many hints for this game!  Call the Nintendo 
            tip line...hehe!       *- NOW SUPPORTING CONSOLE WARES ! -* SPECIAL SOUNDTRACKER CONFERENCE *

                    .....and don't forget to call!!.....

